3DSP WLAN&BT card
*****************
Copyright (c) 2003-2010, 3DSP Corporation, all rights reserved. 


Note: For compiling the drivers, the following components are required:
	build-essential
	linux-headers-(kernel version)


Extraction and installation
===========================

To extract run:
	#tar zxvf BlueW-2310U_3.0.4_100820.tar.gz 

To compile and install run:
	#cd BlueW-2310U_3.0.4_100820
	#sudo bash Install_3DSPUSB.sh

Starting uWB
============

	Applications -> Accessories -> 3DSP uWB

Starting 3DSP WiFi Radar
========================

	Applications -> Accessories -> 3DSP WiFi Radar


Uninstall the drivers and utilities
===================================
	#sudo bash /usr/local/3DSP/usb/Uninstall_3DSPUSB.sh


Note: If your PC support hotkey, you can edit "HOTKEYFLAG=1" in the file "/usr/local/3DSP/usb/wbusb.conf".


Information
===========
Mailing lists:
        tech-support@3dsp.com.cn

